            </choice>ānā<lb break="no" n="3"/>m mahārājaḥ śrī-hari<subst>
              <del rend="corrected">mm</del>
              <add place="overstrike">v</add>
            </subst>armmā bahu-bhava-kr̥taiḥ puṇyai rājya-śriyaṁ nirupadravāM<!-- 
L3."The original has 'mma' but partially erased so as to show that 'va' is intended." CHECK if markup is OK. 
--><lb n="4"/>prakr̥tiṣu hitaḥ prāpto vyāpto jagad-yaśasākhilaM śruta-jala-nidhiḥ vi<lb break="no" n="5"/>dyā-vr̥ddha-pradiṣṭa-pathi sthitaḥ sva-bala-kuliśāghātocchinna-dviṣa<surplus>ṁ</surplus><pb break="no" n="2r"/><lb break="no" n="6"/>d-vasudhā-dharaḥ<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> sva-rājya-saṁvatsare caturtthe phālguṇa-śukla-trayodaśyāM Ucca-
<lb n="7"/>śr̥ṅgyāM sarvva-jana-mano-hlādana-vacana-karmmaṇā sa pitr̥vyeṇa śiva-
<lb n="8"/>ratha-nāmadh<choice>
              <sic>a</sic>
              <corr>e</corr>
            </choice>yenopadiṣṭaḥ palāśikāyāM bhāradvāja-sagotra-si<sic>ṅ</sic>ha-senā-
<lb n="9"/>pati-sutena mr̥geśena kāritasyārhad-āyatanasya prativarṣam āṣṭāhnika-
<lb n="10"/>mahāmaha-satata-carūpalepana-kriyārtthaṁ tad-avaśiṣṭaṁ sarvva-saṁgha-
						<pb n="2v"/><lb n="11"/>bhojanāyeti suddi-kundūra-viṣaye vasunta-vāṭakaṁ sarvva-parihāra-saṁyutaṁ<!-- 
