<lb n="13"/>kr̥tvā dattavāN<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> ya Enaṁ nyāyato <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>bhirakṣati sa tat-puṇya-phala-bhāg bhavati
<lb n="14"/>yaś cainaṁ rāga-dveṣa-lobha-mohair apaharati sa nikr̥ṣṭatamāṁ gatim avā<pb break="no" n="3r"/><lb break="no" n="15"/>pnoti</p>
